<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML+RDFa 1.1//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en">
<head>
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="hwit-spec.css" />
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
<title>Reference specification for an HWIT container</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Assessment Questionnaire</h1>
<p>To generate statistics for annual auditing, this questionnaire must be issued at the
end of every trimester.</p>
<h2>For completion by staff</h2>
<div id="bag_001" class="hwit_group">
<p>Please generate and distribute one week before end of school to allow for recovery
and processing.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Date</dt>
<dd hwit_fill="true" hwit_edit="true" hwit_check="hwit.checks.common.timetyper.istime">&nbsp;</dd>
</dl>
</div>
<h2>For completion by pupil</h2>
<div id="bag_002" class="hwit_group" hwit_fillany="2">
<p>Please tell us about your sporting activities this term.</p>
<dl>
<dt>Name</dt>
<dd hwit_fill="true" hwit_edit="true">&nbsp;</dd>
<dt>Email</dt>
<dd hwit_edit="true" hwit_check="hwit.checks.common.emailtype.isaddr" >&nbsp;</dd>
<dd><a href="http://www.thuswise.org/hwit/docs" class="hwit_tip"><span>Click here to check your school email address</span></a></dd>
<dd><a href="#item_049">more info...</a></dd>
<dt>Activities</dt>
<dd hwit_edit="true">&nbsp;</dd>
<dd>Fill out any sports or hobbies that take up your time either in or out of school.</dd>
</div>
<h2>References</h2>
<div id="bag_003" class="references">
<dl>
<dt><a id="item_049">Email</a></dt>
<dd>If you don't have an email address yet, ask at reception.</dd>
</dl>
</div>
</body>
</html>
